ns. We also make sure that the serial number...[/inwave_info_item][inwave_info_item title=\"Motorcycle Engine Repair\" icon=\"fa fa-clock-o\" icon_size=\"25\" read_more_text=\"Read More\" link=\"http://inwavethemes.com/wordpress/motohero/services/motorcycle-custom-service/\"]With this service, we conduct various diagnostic assessments of your bike’s engine in order to identify the actual location of faults...[/inwave_info_item][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][inwave_info_item title=\"Oil changes\" icon=\"fa fa-glass\" icon_size=\"25\" read_more_text=\"Read More\" link=\"http://inwavethemes.com/wordpress/motohero/services/oil-changes/\" css=\".vc_custom_1468403360276{margin-bottom: 70px !important;}\"]When your engine starts heating up when in traffic or the moment you realize that you bike performance with regards to its speed is a bit down, our oil change service ...[/inwave_info_item][inwave_info_item title=\"Routine Maintenance\" icon=\"fa fa-bullhorn\" icon_size=\"25\" read_more_text=\"Read More\" link=\"http://inwavethemes.com/wordpress/motohero/services/routine-maintenance/\"]Maintenance services like checking brakes, primary and transmission fluid changes among others are provided by a team of expert mechanics...[/inwave_info_item][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row iw_layout=\"wide-bg\" iw_parallax=\"1\" iw_parallax_overlay=\"0.81\" css=\".vc_custom_1459591668293{background: #000000 url(http://localhost:8686/trucksaoviet/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/parallax-1.jpg?id=341) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}\"][vc_column][inwave_heading title=\"pricing tables\" sub_title=\"services\" style=\"style2\" font_weight_title=\"700\" iw_margin_bottom=\"25\" align=\"center\" iw_margin_top=\"\" preview_style2=\"\" css=\".vc_custom_1467972381049{margin-top: 55px !important;margin-bottom: 55px !important;}\"]Our services have also been categorized into three (3) so as to simplify things