=\"fa fa-check-circle theme-color\"></i>Motorcycle decoration</li>\n 	<li><i class=\"fa fa-check-circle theme-color\"></i>12 months Warranty</li>\n</ul>\n[/inwave_price_box][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row iw_layout=\"wide-bg\" iw_parallax_overlay=\"\" iw_parallax_speed=\"\" css=\".vc_custom_1460609829115{background: #1d1d1d url(http://localhost:8686/trucksaoviet/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/all_services_bg.jpg?id=760) !important;background-position: 0 0 !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;}\"][vc_column][vc_row_inner css=\".vc_custom_1459240645706{margin-top: 60px !important;margin-bottom: 110px !important;}\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][inwave_heading title=\"What you get with each of our services\" sub_title=\"MotoHeros advantages\" preview_style1=\"\" css=\".vc_custom_1468403480789{margin-bottom: 10px !important;}\"]Our team of motorcycle technicians have the requisite qualifications, experience and motivation needed to render the best of maintenance and repair services on a wide range of bikes including all European models together with imported bikes. This means that with us you are always guaranteed of getting the right services that your bike needs in order to be in its best shape and improve its performance drastically.[/inwave_heading][inwave_tabs layout=\"accordion\"][inwave_tab_item title=\"Our Qualifications\"]We boast of having a team of professionals who have the requisite technical know-how needed to provide our customers with what they really want. This level of experience in all areas of motorcycle repairs and services together with our goal of satisfying our customers makes us the best shop to come to for all your motorcycle needs.[/inwave_tab_item][inwave_tab_item title=\"Our Capabilities\"]We have a team of motorcycle experts who have specialized in various areas of motorcycle repairs and customizations. This allows us to always have an expert who is c