(85, 1, '2016-03-29 09:04:16', '2016-03-29 09:04:16', '[vc_row][vc_column css=\".vc_custom_1460198018183{margin-bottom: 25px !important;}\"][inwave_comparision_slider before=\"467\" after=\"449\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"5/12\"][inwave_heading title=\"Custom Motorcycles\" font_size_content=\"\" preview_style1=\"\"]Under our repairs and maintenance services, we also have a unique service that deals specifically with custom motorcycles.\n\nWe undertake the creation of a number of custom-made bikes that which are always named after some of Great Britain’s best automotives, aeronautics and maritime history. The reason why we prefer to go with such names is to give credit to those who first came up with such authentic ideas. You can therefore come and have a look at the custom-made motorcycles and select the one that suits your bike tastes.\n\nAside our own custom-made Great Britain inspired motorcycles; we also make room for customers who prefer to have their bikes designed and made in peculiar way to come forward with their ideas whilst we offer them our skills and knowledge. Here, we specifically work to turn a paper-based design of a customer into pure steel. [/inwave_heading][inwave_button style=\"button2\" button_text=\"Get in touch\" button_size=\"button-small\" shape=\"rounded\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"7/12\"][inwave_heading title=\"What we offer ?\" preview_style1=\"\" css=\".vc_custom_1468551542070{margin-bottom: 15px !important;}\"]MotoHero provides you with qualified and highly experienced technicians who work closely with you to transform that design on a sheet of paper into an awesome and classy masterpiece of a bike. We just do not offer high end builds but everything that is involved in their design and creation like;[/inwave_heading][inwave_tabs layout=\"accordion\"][inwave_tab_item title=\"Custom Paint\" font_size_title=\"14\"]MotoHero can provide the whole custom motorcycle package but we know that the first thing that get